Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:08.03,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Wow, love that blazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:11.03,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,You'd look right at home on a TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:11.84,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:12.70,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.79,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,It looks great on ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:17.16,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,You're our pride and joy, Mitsumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:18.80,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Pride and joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.81,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Anyway, I gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.66,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Can't be late for the entrance \Nceremony, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.29,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.88,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yeah, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.09,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\b0\c&H7D7F7A&\frz357.9\fax-0.02\pos(318.5,50)}Call Ended
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:31.26,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'm Iwakura Mitsumi, fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:38.44,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,And my life as a Tokyo \Nhigh schooler starts today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:19.17,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I came here from a tiny, remote town \Non the border of Ishikawa Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:22.17,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Mitsumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:27.66,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'll be back for summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.31,DefaultTop,TACCHAN,0,0,0,,Break a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.47,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.86,Default,TACCHAN,0,0,0,,I wish I coulda sent you off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.00,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Haha, I know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:41.14,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,The nearest train line got shut down \Nmore than a decade ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.75,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,My middle school only had \Neight students in my year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.02,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Here, Mitsumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.68,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Fumi-chan and I have been \Ntogether since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:49.94,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.31,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,I know you like pandas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:54.73,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,If you see Liang Liang, send me pics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.18,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,She's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.19,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.96,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Growing up with my best friend. \NHow cool is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.94,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs12\b0\frz270\pos(372,170)\fscx90\frx10\3c&H501F63&\bord2}Alarm\N\N\N\N\N\N{\3c&HDACF04&}Snooze\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\3c&H744F75&}Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.31,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Heh. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.07,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Listen, Mitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.49,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Change trains at the third stop, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.80,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,This is Nao-chan, my dad's sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.77,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,If anyone strange talks to you, \Njust ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.73,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,She's taking care of me while I'm in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.66,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,You worry too much, Nao-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:07.83,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Can you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:11.56,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,You only just found out that there's \Nmore than one railway company!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.43,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,I wish I could go with you, \Nbut my work starts early today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.31,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:19.95,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,My intuition tells me that today \Nwill be nothing short of perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.53,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(483,1)\blur0.2\fs40\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E44EF&\frz10.89\move(196,136,195.52,129.24,24,1901)\fsp1}Confi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.53,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(483,1)\blur0.2\fs40\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4E44EF&\frz348.7\move(480,136,481.91,129.98,24,1901)\fsp1}dent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.45,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.72,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,It won't just be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:31.05,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,There will be zero screwups for the \Nentirety of my time in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:35.33,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Why? Because I have \Na clear road map for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.50,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I will obviously go to Tokyo U,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.72,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,attend law school, \Nand graduate as valedictorian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.16,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'll join the Ministry of Internal Affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:45.58,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,and build a career there providing \Nkey solutions to rural depopulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.42,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,After I retire, I'll return to my \Nhometown and become mayor there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:52.89,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,using the knowledge from my career \Nto greatly improve our finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.96,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,And when I die, I'll have my ashes \Nscattered in the Sea of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:05:02.49,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,In the next three years, I'll develop \Nthe brains I need to fulfill those ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:06.65,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,However, my family doesn't\Nreally get it, which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.26,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,Are you having fun at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.94,Default,MITSUMIDAD,0,0,0,,Made any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.09,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,They'll probably worry about those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.96,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,so I'll try to put them at ease, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.24,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Just wait and see, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.09,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Ikajima Town's prodigy, your pride and joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.57,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,will return to you as a total big shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:27.01,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Third stop, third stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:34.60,Default,EMCEE,0,0,0,,The entrance ceremony for Tsubame \NWest High School will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.45,Default,EMCEE,0,0,0,,Please welcome the new first-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.23,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Hey, Sousuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.59,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.73,DefaultItalics,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Changing trains now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.30,DefaultItalics,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Taking it easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.97,DefaultItalics,MUKAI,0,0,0,,The entrance ceremony's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.24,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.14,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Maybe I should just go home, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.73,DefaultItalics,MUKAI,0,0,0,,At least try to get here, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.41,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.08,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I probably won't make...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.42,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,She's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.13,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.76,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,A girl in our uniform. \NShe's stuck to the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.65,DefaultItalics,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,She crazy, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.76,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Beats me. Why don't you ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.85,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,I gotta go, so I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.87,Default,MTEACHER,0,0,0,,Are you a first-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:14.56,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.88,Default,MTEACHER,0,0,0,,The others have already entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.72,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was fighting for my life in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.72,Default,MTEACHER,0,0,0,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.48,Default,MUKAI,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.34,Default,MTEACHER,0,0,0,,You still can't reach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.48,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.10,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.36,Default,MTEACHER,0,0,0,,What's going on with Class 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.04,FlashbackTop,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Huh? Where am I? \NDo I go that way? This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.24,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.29,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Got caught in rush hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.03,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,And got sick from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.79,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,This wasn't the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.64,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I wanna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.10,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.66,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.83,DefaultItalics,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.31,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Actually, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.98,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.20,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,H...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.49,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:17.19,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,How many years has it been \Nsince I spoke to a stranger my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:17.87,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:21.12,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,How do I get to school from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.72,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Oh, you're lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.52,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I'm running late, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.60,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:41.01,Default,PRINCIPAL,0,0,0,,High school, college, and employment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:44.39,Default,PRINCIPAL,0,0,0,,They're, uh... all about\Nthe people you meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.15,Default,PRINCIPAL,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:49.65,Default,PRINCIPAL,0,0,0,,After passing our rigorous \Nentrance exams, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.88,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Oh, really? You're from Ishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:53.92,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.95,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Which city?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:55.67,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.90,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I've never been to Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.81,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,What if I don't make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:04.96,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(772,977)\blur0.2\b0\fs12\frz346.4\fax-0.25\frx15\pos(245.5,115.5)}Home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:02.43,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I know I'm gonna get \Na call from home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.54,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,They'll ask how the entrance ceremony went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.50,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,If I tell the truth, they'll worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.76,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Should I lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.44,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,About all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:15.34,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.30,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,It's just the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.81,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Maybe that's all it is to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.31,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,W-Wait, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.19,DefaultItalicsTop,PA,0,0,0,,We will soon be making \Na brief stop at Miyamaeyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.19,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Oh, here's our stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.38,DefaultItalicsTop,PA,0,0,0,,The doors on the right side will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.57,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(276,1)\c&HA2FAE8&\3c&H888C8B&\bord1.5\fs16\frz35.26\fax0.15\pos(578.5,180.5)}Touch here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.74,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,It's about a ten-minute walk from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.62,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,But you're in a rush, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.11,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Wanna run?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.26,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Dad. Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.12,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Maharu. Kippei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.77,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Granny. Satonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:51.26,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Omiso. Oshio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.79,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Everything in Tokyo moves at lightning speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:59.44,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I got swallowed by its waves. \NI panicked, made things worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.64,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,and in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.52,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,It's straight down this road. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.16,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I lashed out at this kind, helpful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:15.20,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I feel like I've seen my own \Ntrue colors in just half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.66,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.50,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Y-You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.25,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'm... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.69,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,But for now, I'm gonna forget all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.07,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,and run for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:45.04,Episode Title,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\pos(613,311.5)}Scene 01: Sparkling-Fresh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:48.54,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.07,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Iwakura-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.25,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,...es...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.81,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Shima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.13,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Yes. Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.52,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Sor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.05,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,There, there. I'm glad you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.13,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Wait, are you okay, Iwakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.77,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Did I... make...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:03.64,DefaultItalics,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.72,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Yes, you're just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.85,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Be sure to thank the person \Nwe asked to sub in for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.33,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I will. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:11.48,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:15.10,Default,EMCEE,0,0,0,,Representing the incoming class, \NIwakura Mitsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.07,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.39,DefaultItalics,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,You're top of the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.46,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Urk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.32,DefaultItalics,PRINCIPAL,0,0,0,,"Urk"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.62,DefaultItalics,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Wait, did she forget her script?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.55,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(655,1)\bord2\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\c&H434343&\3c&HCEDADA&\move(163.5,157.5,171,153,30,2741)}Speech
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.41,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,As the warmth of spring rolls in,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:56.48,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,we 216 students stand here at the entrance \Nceremony for Tsubame West High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:12:02.62,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,On behalf of my class, I would like to \Nthank you all for this wonderful ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.62,DefaultTop,STUDENTA,0,0,0,,She memorized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.57,DefaultTop,STUDENTB,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:08.06,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Our hearts are filled with hopes and fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:12.42,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,just like the sakura trees in the school \Ncourtyard, with flowers yet to blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.81,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,The experience of overcoming \Nthe tough entrance exams
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:18.93,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,will give us confidence and strength \Nto overcome the days ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.04,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Haha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:24.81,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,None of us could have made it this far alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:29.30,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,We must remember the support we \Nreceived from our families and friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.29,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,try to live up to their expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:35.29,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,and in our time at Tsubame West, \Nthink for ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:43.40,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'm blessed to join a school that values \Nindependence, individuality, and autonomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.48,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,And, last but not least,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:48.66,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,to the teachers and the older students:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.90,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,We hope that you will watch over \Nand guide us new students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.02,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.48,DefaultItalics,PRINCIPAL,0,0,0,,She didn't blink once!
