Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.11,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Three. {/int}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.46,Default,RANDOM,0,0,0,,Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.77,Default,KOSHINO,0,0,0,,Oh, the puker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.89,Default,JOUGASAKI,0,0,0,,This is concerning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.34,Default,SUDA,0,0,0,,The puker, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.74,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Day one, and I'm the puker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.46,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,But wait, I can salvage that if I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:55.56,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(107,101)\fs40\bord4\fnTimes New Roman\c&H5A5F58&\3c&HEBF2E9&\pos(62,58)}3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.90,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, I listen to them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.59,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,Aren't they great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.37,Default,KAWATANI,0,0,0,,Hey, let's trade contact details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.77,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,Really? I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.68,Default,KAWATANI,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.38,DefaultTop,MIKA,0,0,0,,Hah, what is this sticker? It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:08.24,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,W-Wow. I should learn from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.32,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:13.21,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I-It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.71,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:20.64,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I feel like she just brushed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:24.85,DefaultTop,MIKA,0,0,0,,By the way, did you watch their \NPinsta Live a couple of days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:23.10,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Iwakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.76,DefaultTop,MIKA,0,0,0,,I only realized towards the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.17,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Guess we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.66,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Shima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.17,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,That's right. You feeling any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.43,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Much better now that I hurled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.56,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Oh, good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.17,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:42.65,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I loved your speech. You bossed it up out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.20,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,This guy's a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.20,DefaultTop,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,You weren't even reading notes, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.51,DefaultTop,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I could never write a speech \Nlike that to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:49.42,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm suddenly even \Nfinding his face lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.36,DefaultTop,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I really thought you were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.95,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Is it because he helped me so much today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:56.58,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Or is Tokyo just filled with \Ndreamy people like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.33,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an5\bord0\blur0.5\p1\c&HF8F9F6&\3c&H626564&\bord1.2\fscx81\fscy35\pos(411.5,115)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.33,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\c&H555757&\3c&HF6F9F6&\b0\pos(408,125.5)}*It isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.33,DefaultItalics,MIKAOTHERS,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, major stud alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.86,DefaultItalics,KAWATANI,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem too conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.09,DefaultItalics,MOTOBAYASHI,0,0,0,,Wonder if he has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.66,DefaultItalics,MINE,0,0,0,,He wasn't in the procession, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.95,DefaultItalics,JOUGASAKI,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:09.08,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Iwakura-san, let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.34,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Oh, give me your ID and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.48,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I'll text you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.35,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs40\t(28,2990,\fscx76.92\fscy76.92)\fnTimes New Roman\3c&H97EFF7&\bord4\blur4\move(628.5,178.5,505.15,121.73,28,2990)}Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.43,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fscx76.92\fscy76.92\t(21,1064,\fscx74.43\fscy74.43)\fnTimes New Roman\move(505.15,121.73,490.4,114.29,21,1064)\3c&H97EFF7&\bord4\blur4}Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:15.85,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,394)\fs40\fscx74.43\fscy74.43\fnTimes New Roman\pos(490.4,114.29)\3c&H97EFF7&\bord4\blur4}Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.56,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,Gimme your ID, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.62,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Egashira Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:26.57,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,I sit right behind you, so I wanna \Nget to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.92,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I guess my timing was just off earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:31.79,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.49,Default,MIKA,0,0,0,,You're Mitsumi-chan? That's a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.58,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Take your seats, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.92,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late. I had a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.83,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:47.11,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,I'm Hanazono Sakura, \Nand I'm in charge of Class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:52.36,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,This is my first time as homeroom teacher, \Nso I'm sure I'll need your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.76,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,but I promise you I'll do my best! \NI'm looking forward to working with you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.22,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Today, I'll give you a simple \Nintro to your textbooks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.85,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,and you'll fill out these profile sheets. \NAfter that, you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.18,Default,SAKURA,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, you'll introduce \Nyourselves to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.07,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.74,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I wonder what my classmates are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.54,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'd like to build some solid \Nrelationships with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.66,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,And that's about it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:24.57,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,No major incidents. \NMy day was a total success.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.54,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Good for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:31.45,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I was so nervous, I couldn't \Nrespond to people who talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:34.30,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,It's just the first day. \NYou'll be fine, Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:38.30,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Ya think? Did ya manage to talk to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.61,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Get this. I made two friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:44.15,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! What're they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:46.35,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,A cute, stylish girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.96,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,and a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:50.73,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Whoa! A guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.07,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,No way! How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.80,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,He helped me this morning when I was los—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:57.57,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,er, was close to going the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.11,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,And we wound up in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.51,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Wow... Is he hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.28,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:06.45,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I guess. I've never met \Nanyone like him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.44,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Very dapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.34,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,Whoa, lucky you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.60,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,But, man, I'd be so lonely \Nif you got a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:15.09,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Come on, quit jumping the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.93,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,I better give it my all from tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.83,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.15,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:22.75,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Oh, Nao-chan's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.04,DefaultItalics,FUMI,0,0,0,,I'll letcha go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:28.21,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Oh, and take care of my siblings, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.11,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're gonna miss having me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.70,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.22,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Nao-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.12,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.79,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,How was the entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:39.99,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.20,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Really? Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.12,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Were you on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.83,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yeah, was talking to Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.89,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,She's feeling helpless \Non her own, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:52.39,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,She always has her head in the clouds, \Nso I worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.09,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.51,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Come, let's eat while we chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.18,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,I bought dinner from \Na fancy deli to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.64,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.79,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,A deli? Wow, these sides are stylin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.03,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,This place makes the yummiest stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:10.26,DefaultItalics,NAO,0,0,0,,Do kids even say "stylin'" these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.36,Default,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.11,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.20,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Satonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.36,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,Hey there, Fumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.14,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Brought you some radishes from Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.49,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,These are so fresh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.57,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,Oh, do your folks need any asparagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.71,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,I'll fetch some in two \Nshakes of a lamb's tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.41,Default,MAHARU,0,0,0,,Fumi-chan, Fumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.91,Default,MAHARU,0,0,0,,Didya phone Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.04,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,I just did, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.13,Default,KIPPEI,0,0,0,,She say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.58,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.63,Default,MAHARU,0,0,0,,Like, she tells us her day went perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:43.20,Default,MAHARU,0,0,0,,but we were thinking she probably \Ngot lost at the station or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.58,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,I was worried about the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:50.95,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,She's got a screw loose when it comes \Nto anything 'sides her studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:51.70,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.92,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,Wow, that's a lot. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.90,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:19:00.18,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,She was happily saying \Nshe made some new pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.26,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,And I'll phone her regularly \Nto check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.29,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,Thank you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:06.02,Default,FUMI,0,0,0,,I'll be off, then. Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.49,Default,MITSUMIMUM,0,0,0,,I'd feel a lot better \Nif Fumi-chan were there with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.94,Default,MAHARU,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.98,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,How was your entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:19.00,Default,BOYA,0,0,0,,My class is looking pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:19.95,Default,GIRLA,0,0,0,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.84,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,Mine had this awkward mood from day one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:25.11,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Hey, don't take my shrimp! I only had four...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.16,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,Don't be a cheapskate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.52,Default,BOYA,0,0,0,,Your uniform is real cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.84,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,How about you, Sousuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.45,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:32.65,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Yeah. How's your little elite school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.74,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I overslept, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.53,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,That was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.59,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,You didn't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:39.65,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,No, I did. I ran from the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.11,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,Who, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.61,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:47.62,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I thought there wouldn't be a chance in hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:51.22,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,but the principal's speech \Napparently went forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.29,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,so we ended up making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:58.74,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,That was kinda fun, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.82,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Was it with a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.38,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Oh, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:05.57,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Lemme out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.27,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.59,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.47,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.48,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Was it really a girl? That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.91,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.98,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Nah, just thought I'd go home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.08,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Wouldn't want to be late tomorrow, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.13,Default,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.57,Default,RIRIKA,0,0,0,,The heck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.41,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:31.48,Default,CHRIS,0,0,0,,Something must've made him \Nreally happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.56,DefaultItalics,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:44.09,DefaultItalics,SOUSUKE,0,0,0,,I might as well enjoy my high school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.65,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,The night lights are so bright here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:58.44,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Today's mistakes don't count. \NIt was only my first day, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:04.09,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Also, I did study for the post-entrance exam \Nand did a bunch of my spring homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.07,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,All good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.41,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'll be fine from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.78,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:20.18,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Self-introductions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:23.39,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,Won't be a problem, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:29.26,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,But maybe I should figure out \Nwhat I'm gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:31.76,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,First impressions are key.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:35.14,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,I'll prepare multiple options \Nbased on the class's mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.62,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Mitsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.19,DefaultItalics,MITSUMI,0,0,0,,First impressions are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:05.24,Default,NAO,0,0,0,,Yikes!
